{"tid":661052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領銅鑼灣！中國人SOGO集體掃貨 港人嘆買份母親節禮物都難","createTime":"2018-05-11T08:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T05:00:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d456b5ed54f5c0b04d0a148dd1b317906f72a076","tid":661052,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣崇光百貨公司感謝祭，不少內地客聞風湧至，迫爆百貨公司各樓層外，搶購化妝品的人龍更重重包圍百貨公司外的大街小巷。警方下午出動藍帽子驅散阻塞通道的內地客。<br />\n<br />\n感謝周年慶首日已有約幾千名內地客在百貨公司輪候打蛇餅。人流不僅阻塞東角道及駱克道行人路，不少顅客及途人更被迫要行馬路。有代購客疑似集團式行動，在行人路及公司門外執貨分貨。<br />\n<br />\n下午警方派出幾名警員勸喻阻路人士離開，也有交通督導員到場，但有警車及救護車也要緩慢通過，其後藍帽子到場增援，用擴音器叫阻塞通道人士不要停留。<br />\n<br />\n有一心想買護膚品給母親，祝賀媽媽母親節快樂的本港市民抱怨，內地人繼搶奶粉、演唱會票、炒樓之後，現在想買母親節禮品可能也要找內地人代購。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180511/large/1526025107_923c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F1526025107_923c.jpg&h=76861a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180511/large/1526025216_5ddd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F1526025216_5ddd.jpg&h=858409be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180511/large/1526025220_ce5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F1526025220_ce5b.jpg&h=858fd353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180511/large/1526025228_d69a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F1526025228_d69a.jpg&h=cc2fdc01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180511/large/1526025339_03c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180511%2Flarge%2F1526025339_03c6.jpg&h=a39c6bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180511/58179718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58179718&d=cvraUpSWqjSd0pn6kM4YLjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=cefb573e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180511%2F58179718&h=2e259b6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180511/58179718</a>"},{"pid":"80ff243a55f57c7070ae179b6d1ca727eefe3fbe","tid":661052,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3653eaf23cd776232ca9ffcbe2d63a5f230f4b","tid":661052,"uid":131041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"thankful week 正常"},{"pid":"fe514884e46e610de49a646571a3d20ea977b10f","tid":661052,"uid":179467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"十足十Black Friday madness <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed20b47d84d5251b5d556f4840b5e2f046afeac","tid":661052,"uid":10707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"佔領SOGO，買到斷貨，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf11511cd386ecf79befef103f95b18c6c936326","tid":661052,"uid":76310,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"要不是中國照顧你，你地香港早就完蛋了"},{"pid":"b116e286eefca87f39535ba34bd0b9f31954cf04","tid":661052,"uid":47080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7ed20b47d84d5251b5d556f4840b5e2f046afeac","tid":661052,"uid":10707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1